Copper Top is an awesome spot for breakfast and lunch.
I no longer live in Madison but ate at Copper Top dozens of times when I was in high school and college there and always try to go back whenever I visit Madison.
Don't expect anything fancy...I didn't rate this 5 stars because the food was the best I've ever had.
I rated this 5 stars because the service is always great, your coffee is always full, you get your food really fast, and you get a great amount of food for the price you pay.

